ope TEIform=\"biblScope\">237</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0284.tlg001.perseus-grc1:46(3).38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristid.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">46(3).38</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n92646.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cause to gush forth</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅταν . . κρηναῖον ἐξ ἄμμοιο-ήση γάνος</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lyc.\">Lyc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">247</biblScope></bibl></cit>. (In signf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11</biblScope> </bibl> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥυβδέω</foreign> shd. perh. be written, cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀναρροιβδέω</foreign>; signf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope> </bibl> is found also in <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπορροιβδέω, ἐπιρροιβδέω</foreign>.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}